  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CalculatorServer
    CalculatorServer is the interface of the actual implementation of the corresponding RMI Object, and it extends RMIRemoteStub for RMI Stub creation.
    ZipCodeServer
    ZipCodeServer is the interface of the actual implementation of the corresponding RMI Object, and it extends RMIRemoteStub for RMI Stub creation.
